<div id="review_1837153551" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1837153551" />
    <a title="Amanda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5476515-amanda"><img alt="Amanda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1588721342p2/5476515.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1837153551?book_show_action=true">Dec 31, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amanda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amanda" href="/user/show/5476515-amanda">Amanda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1837153551" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2500105306818833664">4.5 stars - This was a really fantastic book to finish off the year. This book is beautiful and heartbreaking and my writing skills could never do it justice. If you are at all interested in Iceland and Scandinavian lit this is a must read. It is a slow burn and takes some patience. It is a book I would like to revisit at least parts of in the future. I will be thinking about these characters and what it really means to be an independent person for a long time.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review1837153551">
